%html
  %head
    %title Welcome to yamx
  %body
    %h1 YAMX
    %p
      YAMX is simple management extension that can be used for checking status
      of all your apps.  Its build using REST-style API integration between apps
      and the management server.

    %h2 Currently known server and apps
    - @list.each do |i|
      %p= "#{i.app_name} running in  #{i.hostname}/#{i.ipaddr} "
